The U.S. Treasury said it will sell12.8 billion dlrs of three and six-month bills at its regularauction next week.    The March 23 sale, to be evenly divided between the threeand six month issues, will result in a paydown of 2.875 billiondlrs as maturing bills total 15.68 billion dlrs.    The bills will be issued March 26. Reuter&#3;